Job Posting Title:   SE_System Architect_Senior Expert
Description:

Develop end to end functional specifications and requirements on system level in line with the overall product requirements. Manage global function targets and coordinate the endtoend function owners. Assist and recommend component selection efforts and judge suitability to design requirements. Support in defining complete system solution and integration at complete system and product level. On Senior Expert level the employee is recognized both within and outside the organization as thought leader in area of expertise.
- Master contributor to the education and development of others within Volvo Group
- Has uptodate understanding of market trends and able to leverage strong internal and external networks to remain ahead of the game
- An ambassador of the TD/BA who adds value through clear articulation of fresh, futurefocused links between their area of expertise and other parts of the industry.

Senior Expert: Position typically requires 12+ years of relevant experience. Recognized as an expert in their discipline

Volvo Group is an equal opportunity employer that values diversity in our workplace and we welcome all applicants regardless of age, ethnicity, gender or cultural background.

Job Posting Start Date:   2024-02-14
Job Posting End Date:   2024-08-15
Location:   Göteborg
Job Family:   Mechanical Architecture & System
Price: 918 sek/h

